{"tid":763080,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"貿易戰第二輪2000億25%","createTime":"2018-07-31T23:45:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-01T00:37:06.000Z","uid":50457,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"71d2f8c0471637995a29c48c6e80e1cd55ad8c3f","tid":763080,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T23:45:39.000Z","msg":"特朗普擬提高2000億美元對華商品關稅稅率至25%<br />\n<br />\n外媒引述3名知情人士指，美國特朗普政府計劃提高對2,000億美元中國進口商品加徵關稅的稅率，由之前建議的10%，大幅提高至25%，此舉勢將令中英貿易談判增添壓力。知情人士稱，有關方案尚未最終確認，並需通過公眾諮詢。 <br />\n<br />\n於7月初，美國已經對340億美元的中國進口商品加徵25%的關稅，另一批價值160億美元中國進口商品加徵關稅的計劃將於周三結束審批。 <br />\n<br />\n美國上月已經公布了對華加徵關稅的2,000億美元商品清單，目前正處於為期兩個月的公開意見徵求期，而有關新關稅所涉產品的聽證會定於8月20至23日舉行。報道指，特朗普可能會在聽證會之前宣布提高關稅稅率，而他已經指示美國貿易代表萊蒂澤負責相關工作。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180801/mobile/bkn-20180801070329536-0801_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20180801%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180801070329536-0801_00842_001.html&d=W67X%2BWn2kt8mU7f9FemoottKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=f1cd9293\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180801/mobile/bkn-20180801070329536-0801_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"d83df37e3282e5545629053bd6a1db39ab7c3967","tid":763080,"uid":22876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T00:12:13.000Z","msg":"今朝TVB新聞係咁講話準備和解和談<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53995eacf56f1035203835b4fc33f14da8f22bc4","tid":763080,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T00:32:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dbfe32241fc6cabc1af0d9c926e0b9ba9e53332","tid":763080,"uid":59451,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T00:37:06.000Z","msg":"個頭又話傾 呢頭又話徵 即係點 好亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}